      • mergeVariable

        public AbstractVariable mergeVariable(AbstractVariable variable)

        Persists the given variable to the database using JPA merge semantics.

        As stated in getByKey, changes are usually automatically persisted. Call this only to persist a brand-new object or to persist changes made after the transaction in which the object was loaded.

        Note that the given object is not added to the persistence context, but the returned object is. If you want to modify further state, use the returned object.

        Parameters:
        variable - represents the state to persist
